[SN]TITLE[SN]
Cardiff Half Marathon: Gareth 'Alfie' Thomas back to train three women's teams for run

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A year after training a group of 16 unfit ladies from Deri to run the Cardiff Half Marathon, former Wales rugby international Gareth 'Alfie' Thomas has been back to do it all again with three new teams.

